{
  "stem": "2906.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They gave us this-- the corn that you make a little bit of flour and they were using the same thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they had a lot of things to do, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they used to bring us back to the kolkhoz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were a lot of families.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They used to cook and eat, and I used to go and bring them water from the lake.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I used to bring them water, and I was too shy to say, give me some food to eat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I used to bring the water and go away and just sit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, you go for [INAUDIBLE], after work and-- and you think maybe they'll give you something to eat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So some people after they do this, they used to say, give me something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was young and I was too shy, and I didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I worked, and I didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "From there one time, they sent us to another place, to the railroad.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the railroad, we [? act-- ?] you-- you cannot make a shovel do it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The earth is so hard there that you got like-- they used to call it [? kitman ?], it's like a hack, you hack there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I didn't have already shoes because I made myself in-- shoes from rags.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was colder there, and we worked there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And by the railroad, there were beets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At night we used to go and get a couple beets and cook them and eat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But if they would catch us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They would kill us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You're not supposed to-- you know, it's like you take away something from-- We stayed in a house, all the three girls of us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And one day I said I cannot go--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Russian people, used to live, a little house.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
